      "title": "One of a Kind Hand Carved Wooden Spoons / Kitchen Utensils / Edition 10 Pear Wood No 073-078",
      "description": "A new edition of hand carved wooden spoons made from pear wood, one of the finest european hardwoods. The wood features warm tones, a fine grained structure, and has a wonderfully tactile feel. These spoons are sturdy yet lightweight, they feel velvety smooth, and are made to be a lifelong companion in the kitchen. Each wooden spoon is one of a kind and is rubbed with organic walnut oil.\r\n\r\nChoose one or more from this edition of six:\r\n\r\n- No. 073 - length 13" (33cm) - straight handle\r\n- No. 074 - sold\r\n- No. 075 - length 13" (33cm) - straight handle\r\n- No. 076 - sold\r\n- No. 077 - sold\r\n- No. 078 - length 11,8" (30cm) - straight handle\r\n\r\nThe spoons are easy to care. Just rinse and towel dry. Rub it with walnut or olive oil or any other food save oil every once in a while.\r\n\r\nLESS & MORE Kitchen Tools are hand carved from dry hardwood by me, Hannah, using traditional tools and techniques. Every single spoon, spatula, or bowl is unique. I love the little irregularities of a handmade spoon that lend an individual character to every single piece. Thats why I don´t use patterns to duplicate an item.\r\n\r\nAs an experienced and passionate cook I like my kitchen utensils being highly functional. A handle should be smooth and just feel good to hold. Smooth and gentle curves should allow me to perfectly reach the edges of a pot or pan. As I don´t like their "hair standing on end" after their first contact with a hot meal I treat the utensils with boiling water and sandpaper several times in the course of production before they get rubbed with organic walnut oil.\r\n\r\n♠ PLEASE NOTE: Nut oil may affect people with nut allergies, even when used as a finish.\r\n\r\n♠ SHIPPING\r\nItem ships by registered priority airmail with tracking number.\r\nCOMBINED INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING: If you are overcharged for shipping when you purchase multiple items, we will refund the difference when we ship your products.\r\n\r\n♠ OUR ITEMS AS GIFTS - LET US DO THE JOB FOR YOU!\r\nAll our products come carefully wrapped in 100% environment friendly and compostable packaging. Ready for gift giving. If you wish we send gifts directly to the recipient. We can include a personal note as well as exclude a receipt. Order as normal and enter the lucky recipients information (shipping address and personal note) in the "Message to Seller" box when you check out.\r\n\r\n♠ FAQs\r\nWhen ordering please check our store policies: \r\nhttp://www.etsy.com/shop/lessandmore/policy\r\n\r\n♠ FIND MORE OF OUR KITCHEN AND SERVING UTENSILS HERE: \r\nhttps://www.etsy.com/shop/lessandmore?section_id=14171219\r\n\r\n♠ HOW TO BUY ON ETSY: \r\nhttp://www.etsy.com/help/article/339\r\n\r\nReturn to our store: http://www.etsy.com/shop/lessandmore",
